OL,7,FThe widow of a police officer who
OL,8,Fdied after being hit by a train as he
OL,9,Ftried to save a distressed man on the
OL,10,Ftracks has paid tribute to her
OL,11,F"wonderful" husband who had a "desire
OL,12,Fto help others".
OL,14,FSergeant Graham Saville, who had
OL,15,Frecently been promoted, suffered
OL,16,Fserious injuries in the incident in
OL,17,FBalderton, near Newark-on-Trent, on
OL,18,FThursday 24 August, and died in
OL,19,Fhospital on Tuesday.
OL,3,CSergeant Graham Saville: Widow of
OL,4,Chero officer hit by train says he had
OL,5,Ca 'desire to help others'
